And that's a wrap for the first quarter. There are a lot of things I'd like to call it, but shall resist the urge to curse. But it sucked....big time. Worst quarter for the #DOW since 1987. It dropped another 410 today. But hey, the market's up nearly 20% from the low on 3/23
